    "form_header_text": "FY27 Programmatic and Language Requests - Office of Congresswoman Emily Randall (WA-06)",
    "form_instructions_text": "Thank you for your interest in the federal appropriations process. Please submit this form no later than two weeks prior to the relevant subcommittee's deadline. Our deadlines may change once the Appropriations Committee posts their deadlines. Additional information can be found at appropriations.house.gov. There are three types of appropriations requests Members can submit to the House Appropriations Committee: Community Project Funding (CPF) Requests, Programmatic Requests, and Language Requests. This request form is ONLY for programmatic and language requests. There will be a separate form to submit community project funding requests once we receive more information from the Appropriations Committee.",
